In the Matter of Kenneth Linn, a Suspended Attorney.

[— NYS2d —]

—Motion to confirm the Determination of the Hearing Panel granted and respondent reinstated as an attorney and counselor-at-law in the State of New York, effective the date hereof. No opinion. Concur — Rosenberger, J. P., Williams, Mazzarelli, Wallach and Lerner, JJ.
